Package: makeJAGSmask
Type: Package
Title: Construct a habitat matrix for use with SECR analysis in JAGS or BUGS
Version: 0.0.6.9006
Date: 2018-07-01
Imports: MASS, abind
Suggests: secr, sp, rgeos
Author: Mike Meredith
Maintainer: Mike Meredith <mmeredith@wcs.org>
Description: Functions to create habitat masks for spatially explicit capture-recapture (SECR) analysis in BUGS or JAGS. Currently this is done by converting a mask prepared by the \pkg{secr} package.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: no